calculateChecksum

public short calculateChecksum()
Calculates the checksum of this ICMP packet. The checksum field is the 16 bit one's complement of the one's complement sum of all 16 bit words in the header. For purposes of computing the checksum, the value of the checksum field is zero.

Returns:
Checksum
